data.description: This house in Newport seems like a fantastic find, offering affordability, coziness, and convenient amenities like the newer propane furnace, newer hot water heater, and nearby park.  Its location near downtown shopping and restaurants adds to its appeal.  If you're considering this property, I'm here to help with any questions you might have.  To access the 2nd bedroom, you need to walk through the 1st bedroom.  Please be sure to schedule showings during daylight.  The power is turned off, so please bring a flashlight to look at the basement and attic.  Thanks for your interest!
